snippet.title: Techno Banter - Launch Trailer | PC, PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Techno Banter, the witty story of a club bouncer's misadventures is available on PC and Consoles now!

You're the bouncer of the Green Door club, where every decision matters. Reject the unworthy of partying with clever retorts, explore a neon-lit city, and immerse yourself in the Berlin-like city's underground techno scene. The beat is pumping—are you in?

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2348400/Techno_Banter
PlayStation 5: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10008104
Xbox Series X|S: https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/techno-banter/9NTCXTQ9PJ0Q
Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/techno-banter-switch/
